<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPal7">
<l>antarat tamararkaḷ kūṭṭaṅka ḷivaiyō varuntava muṉivaru marutaru mivarō</l>
<l>intira ṉāṉaiyun tāṉumvan tivaṉō vemperu māṉuṉ kōyiliṉ vācaṟ</l>
<l>cuntarar nerukkavic cātarar nūkka viyakkarum mayaṅkiṉar tiruvaṭi toḻuvāṉ</l>
<l>antaram pāriṭa millaimaṟ ṟituvō varaṅkattam māpaḷḷi yeḻuntaru ḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Are these the crowds of immortals from heaven?</l>
<l>Are these sages of rare penance and the Maruts?</l>
<l>Is this Indra himself come along with [his] elephant?</l>
<l>Our Lord! As the Gandharvas jostle and the Vidyādharas shove</l>
<l rend="indent">at the entrance of Your temple,</l>
<l>the Yakṣas are anxious to worship [Your] sacred feet!</l>
<l>There is no other space [left] in the sky [or on] earth, is there?</l>
<l>O Lord of Raṅgam, do grace to wake up from sleep!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
